and Subs the 13th &amp; 14th grafs, `That wind,' to update records and tighten.</HEAD>
<HEAD>LaserPhoto CX4</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By ROGER PETTERSON</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
